data.description: This cute 3 bedroom, 1 bath, 2 car detached home features a large 3 seasons porch to relax and enjoy a cup of coffee, a good sized fenced in backyard with a wood deck, mature trees, a neat little rotunda area in the basement that could make the perfect wine cellar, many upgrades including a fully remodeled kitchen & appliances-2019, fully remodeled bathroom-2019, new wood plank ceiling and carpet in the master bedroom w/ fresh paint, fresh paint and carpet throughout the upper level, added central air and new furnace-2022, basement was cleaned & sealed w/ a new washer and dryer unit, new pine doors installed 2019, and more. Located in a nice neighborhood conveniently located near schools, parks, walking/biking trails, water, restaurants, shopping, and entertainment. Make your appointment for a showing today!
